---
<section class="section-padding bg-white overflow-hidden relative">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <div class="reveal">
       <span class="text-[60px] font-serif text-[#84A59D]/20 block mb-6 leading-none">“</span>
       <h3 class="text-3xl font-medium text-[#2D3436] italic leading-relaxed sm:text-4xl max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          "Pela primeira vez, senti que não precisava ser perfeita para ser aceita. A terapia me devolveu a paz que eu nem sabia que tinha perdido."
       </h3>
       <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-[#FAF7F2] border border-[#84A59D]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
             <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-[#84A59D]">M.L.</span>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#2D3436]/40">Paciente Acompanhada há 1 ano</span>
       </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Decorative plant image floating -->
  <div class="absolute -right-20 bottom-0 opacity-10 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000 hidden lg:block">
     <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497250681960-ef046c08a56e?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=400" alt="Planta" class="w-64" />
  </div>
</section>
